claim.claim-text:
1. A method for making a semiconductor device, comprising:
providing a semiconductor substrate;
forming a high-k dielectric layer on the substrate, the high-k dielectric layer having first and second regions;
forming an NMOS layer stack on the high-k dielectric layer in the first region, and then subjecting the high-k dielectric layer to nitridation within the second region; and
forming a PMOS layer stack within the second region.
